      img(src="fig/segment.png")
   section
      h1 Problem

      p.ntnupurple Surgery on the 3D Model

      ul
        li.fragment Soft Tissue Deformation (Continuous Changes/Differential Equations)
          ul
            li Muscle, Fat, etc.
        li.fragment Cutting and Tear (Topological Changes/Discrete Events)
