            li Scalpel
        li.fragment Real-Time Interaction
          ul
            li Visualisation and Haptic Feedback
        li.fragment Interaction between Tissue Types 
        li.fragment Interaction with Rigid Bodies
          ul
            li Skeleton, including movement (bending of the knee)


